BILLBOARD MUSIC AWARDS 2022: HOSTS, WINNERS, NOMINEES, PERFORMANCES AND RED CARPET

Christina Aguilera puts on a busty display in a red hot gown while Becky G sizzles in a racy lime lace-up dress at the 2022 Billboard Latin Music Awards Christina Aguilera wore a fiery ensemble to the 2022 Latin Billboard Music Awards, held at the Watsco Center inside the University of Miami in Coral Gables, Florida, on Thursday. The singer, 41, smouldered in a cleavage baring lace red gown that clung to her curves and featured dramatic sleeves and built-in boots. Also at the event was Becky G, 25, who wore a racy lime lace-up dress that showed off her cleavage and trim midsection....read Christina Aguilera and Becky G attend the Billboard Latin Music Awards

Megan Fox and Machine Gun Kelly clarify marriage rumors... as pop punk rapper insists actress 'never felt like my girlfriend' The 36-year-old actress supported her 32-year-old pop punk rapper at the premiere for his documentary Machine Gun Kelly's Life In Pink on Monday night. Megan Fox and Machine Gun Kelly clarify marriage rumors

Cara Delevingne cuts a casual figure during a shopping trip at the Glendale Galleria Mall... after THAT awkward interaction with Megan Thee Stallion Cara Delevingne sported a casual look while indulging in a shopping spree at the Glendale Galleria Mall in Los Angeles on Saturday. Cara Delevingne cuts a casual figure at the Glendale Galleria Mall

A music awards show or a lingerie catwalk? Megan Thee Stallion, Becky G, Latto, Jazelle, Kali Uchis and Teyana Taylor all wear underwear to ceremony It was a big night for music on Sunday at the Billboard Music Awards in Las Vegas. But it looked more like a lingerie fashion show - think the old-school Victoria's Secret catwalk events. Megan Thee Stallion, Becky G, Latto wear lingerie to Billboard Awards

Ed Sheeran and Florence Welch lead the Brit performers at Billboard Music Awards as Cara Delevingne parties at Las Vegas ceremony Brit talent provided some of the stand-out performances at the 2022 Billboard Music Awards in Las Vegas. Ed Sheeran and Florence lead Brit performers at Billboard Awards

Megan Thee Stallion twerks her magic! Rapper wears jaw-dropping sheer catsuit with thong as she leads the red hot performances at the Billboard Awards Megan Thee Stallion took the performances at the 2022 Billboard Music Awards to a whole new level in a racy outfit. Billboard Awards 2022: Megan Thee Stallion performs in racy outfit

Billboard Awards 2022: Becky G flashes skin in one-sleeve shimmery mini dress with ostrich feathers on the red carpet in Las Vegas The singer, born Rebbeca Marie Gomez, wore her dark hair swept back from her face, letting it fall loose down her back. Billboard Awards 2022: Becky G flashes skin in shimmery mini dress

Billboard Awards 2022: Dixie D'Amelio flashes a wide smile while rocking a figure-hugging sage green dress on the glitzy show's red carpet The 20-year-old social media personality appeared to be making the most of her time at the star-studded event, as she flashed a wide smile while posing for several photos before heading in. Billboard Awards 2022: Dixie D'Amelio rocks a figure-hugging dress

Sean 'Diddy' Combs turns Billboard Awards into family affair... as daughter Chance rocks black-feathered mini alongside twins Jessie and D'Lila in matching sequin jumpsuits Sean 'Diddy' Combs turned the 2022 Billboard Music Awards into a family affair, as daughters Chance and twins Jessie and D'Lila hit red carpet in show of support. Sean 'Diddy' Combs' daughters attend Billboard Music Awards with dad

Billboard Music Awards 2022: Doja Cat shocks in $110 gold pasties with her topless black Schiaparelli gown The 26-year-old Freaky Deaky singer-rapper went on to win four trophies - top R&B album, top R&B artist, top R&B female, and top viral song (with SZA) - during the NBC telecast Billboard Music Awards 2022: Doja Cat dons topless Schiaparelli gown

Janet Jackson gets a standing ovation as she presents Mary J Blige with the Billboard Icon Award at the glitzy event in Las Vegas Janet Jackson got a standing ovation as she arrived onstage at the Billboard Music Awards on Sunday night in Las Vegas. Janet Jackson gets a standing ovation at the Billboard Awards

The Kid Laroi wins multiple accolades at the Billboard Music Awards for his hit song Stay featuring Justin Bieber Laroi, 18, whose real name is Charlton Howard, won Top Hot 100 Song, Top Streaming Song and Top Collaboration The Kid Laroi wins multiple accolades at the Billboard Music Awards

Olivia Rodrigo and Kanye West lead the artists honored during the non-televised portion of the 2022 Billboard Music Awards Kanye and Rodrigo were tied with six trophies apiece ahead of the ceremony broadcast live form the MGM Garden Arena in Las Vegas on Sunday. Olivia Rodrigo and Kanye West honored in non-televised part of BBMAs

Is Megan Fox pregnant? Machine Gun Kelly dedicates his song to his 'wife' and 'our unborn child' at Billboard Music Awards Machine Gun Kelly and Megan Fox are sparking pregnancy rumors after his performance at the Billboard Music Awards. Is Megan Fox pregnant? Machine Gun Kelly sings to their 'unborn child'

Beyonce's protégé Chloe Bailey shows off her toned abs in a clingy cut-out leather dress with cheeky thong detail Chloe Bailey looked sensational as she hit the red carpet at the 2022 Billboard Music Awards on Sunday. Billboard Awards 2022: Chloe Bailey shows off abs in a cut-out dress

Mary J. Blige looks fierce at 51 in sexy cut-out dress as she's honored with Icon Award at Billboard Music Awards Mary J. Blige looked incredible as she arrived on the red carpet at the Billboard Music Awards in Las Vegas on Sunday. Mary J. Blige stuns in revealing black dress at Billboard Music Awards

Billboard Awards 2022: Michael Bublé and expectant wife Luisana Lopilato embrace with PDA on red carpet at musical ceremony The Canadian musical artist, 46, grabbed the baby bump of his actress spouse, 34, about three months after the pair revealed their fourth child is on the way. Billboard Awards 2022: Michael Bublé and expecting wife embrace

Billboard Awards worst dressed! Teyana Taylor, Kali Uchis and Miranda Lambert lead the bawdy and bizarre ensembles missing the mark in Las Vegas Teyana Taylor, Kali Uchis and Miranda Lambert were among the stars missing the fashion mark at the 2022 Billboard Music Awards on Sunday night in Las Vegas. Teyana Taylor and Kali Uchis lead Billboard Awards worst dressed

Cara Delevingne gives a glimpse at her midriff in crop-top with wrap around detail as she poses alongside Megan Thee Stallion at the Billboard Awards Cara Delevingne showed looked chic as she playfully posed alongside Megan Thee Stallion at the Billboard Music Awards at the MGM Grand Garden Arena in Las Vegas on Sunday. Billboard Awards 2022: Cara Delevingne gives a glimpse at black attire

Billboard Awards 2022: Megan Thee Stallion shows her curves in halter top and miniskirt in Las Vegas The 27-year-old rapper showed her curves in a sandy halter top and miniskirt on Sunday at the 2022 Billboard Music Awards in Las Vegas. Billboard Awards 2022: Megan Thee Stallion shows curves in halter top

Florence Welch turns heads in a sheer gown and black lace bodysuit as she arrives at the Billboard Music Awards The British singer beamed on the red carpet before taking to the stage to perform at the Las Vegas ceremony. Florence Welch turns heads in a sheer gown and black lace bodysuit

Billboard Awards 2022: Miranda Lambert shows her flare for fashion in tailored denim suit on the red carpet with husband Brendan McLoughlin The 38-year-old performer and her 30-year-old husband kept their arms around each other while they posed for several photos before making their way to the MGM Grand Garden Arena. Billboard Awards 2022: Miranda Lambert poses in tailored denim suit

'I'm boring': Megan Fox reveals plans for sober birthday celebration after Billboard Awards... but says fiance Machine Gun Kelly will 'go off for me' Megan Fox sizzled on the red carpet at the 2022 Billboard Music Awards at MGM Grand Garden Arena in Las Vegas, Nevada. Megan Fox and Machine Gun Kelly attend Billboard Awards 2022

Billboard Awards 2022: Heidi Klum stuns on the red carpet in Las Vegas in yellow slit gown with black knee-high boots The 48-year-old model posed on the red carpet in a yellow shoulderless slit gown, with long black gloves and knee-high black boots rounding out the ensemble. Billboard Awards 2022: Heidi Klum stuns in yellow slit gown in Vegas

Billboard Awards 2022: Latto brings the Big Energy to the red carpet at the awards show in Las Vegas Latto brings the Big Energy to the red carpet for her first ever Billboard Music Awards on Sunday night. Billboard Awards 2022: Latto brings the Big Energy to the red carpet

Billboard Awards 2022: Diddy wears all-white outfit as host promises to 'uncancel the canceled' on 25th anniversary of winning his first BBMA The 52-year-old rapper wore an all-white outfit on Sunday as he promised to 'uncancel the canceled' while hosting the 2022 Billboard Music Awards in Las Vegas. Billboard Awards 2022: Diddy promises to 'uncancel the canceled'

Battle of the busty bombshells! Megan Fox stuns in plunging gown, Doja Cat shocks with nipple pasties and Kylie Jenner puts curves on show in graphic frock at Billboard Awards red carpet The biggest names in the music industry descended upon Las Vegas on Sunday afternoon to celebrate the artists who dominated the charts over the past year at the 2022 Billboard Music Awards. Billboard Awards 2022: Best dressed stars on red carpet

Diddy 'demanded' that Travis Scott perform at the 2022 Billboard Music Awards... his first televised performance since Astroworld tragedy Travis Scott will make his first performance since the Astroworld tragedy in November at the Billboard Music Awards, and it seems to be Diddy's doing. Diddy 'demanded' that Travis Scott perform at 2022 Billboard Awards

Morgan Wallen to perform at the upcoming Billboard Music Awards... after he was caught on tape using a racial slur in 2021 The news about the 28-year-old songwriter was reported on Friday, when it was noted that MRC Live & Alternative executives had decided to allow the singer to appear at the awards ceremony. Morgan Wallen will perform at the upcoming Billboard Music Awards

'I'm the ringmaster!' Sean 'Diddy' Combs announces he'll host and executive produce the Billboard Music Awards next month The 52-year-old rap mogul appeared to be excited about filling both roles in his clip, in which he stepped outside of his house to watch the sunrise and let his neighbors know about his new venture. Sean 'Diddy' Combs will lead the 2022 Billboard Music Awards

'I am truly humbled': Mary J. Blige set to receive the Icon Award at 2022 Billboard Music Awards Mary J. Blige is joining the ranks with an elite group of entertainers. Mary J Blige to receive the Billboard Music Icon Award in May

Karol G turns up glam factor at Billboard Women In Music Awards in red gown and opera gloves inspired by Julia Roberts in Pretty Woman Karol G turned up the glam factor when she strutted her stuff to the Billboard Music Awards in Los Angeles this Wednesday where she was to be given the Rule Breaker Award. Karol pays tribute to Pretty Woman at Billboard Women In Music Awards

Too hot to handle! Summer's sexiest celeb-obsessed trend is a hybrid beach frock that's one part bodysuit one part dress Megan Fox stepped out in one of summer's hottest trends: the beach frock. The sexy number is one part bodysuit and one part dress. The designer label that put the alluring look on the map? PatBo! Summer's sexiest garment is one part bodysuit one part dress

Drake gets VERY close to coffee shop owner Luisa Duran who says he's like 'a brother' as she celebrates his Artist of the Decade win The 34-year-old Canadian rapper was shown getting cozy with coffee shop owner Luisa Duran in a snap she shared Tuesday in honor of him winning Artist Of The Decade. Drake gets VERY close to coffee shop owner Luisa Duran on Instagram

The Weeknd rocks his Super Bowl merchandise hoodie as he heads out on a walk with pals after his big win at the Billboard Music Awards The Weeknd let his Billboard Music Awards success soak in as he headed out for a stroll with his pals in Silver Lake, Los Angeles on Monday. The Weeknd rocks his Super Bowl merch hoodie as he heads out on a walk

Saweetie sips on champagne as she strolls through Beverly Hills in boldly patterned baggy shirt and shorts The rapper, 27, carried a bubblegum pink purse on a shoulder strap and stepped out in embellished sandal heels. Saweetie sips on champagne as she strolls through Beverly Hills

Bling it on! Priyanka Chopra modeled 40 CARATS of diamonds that included a snake watch at the Billboard Music Awards The 38-year-old actress sparkled head-to-toe at the music awards in Los Angeles on Sunday in the fully-sheer Dolce and Gabbana gold gown, complete with Bulgari gemstones. Priyanka Chopra Jonas dazzled in a 40 carats of diamonds

Megan Fox appears to swear and looks frosty alongside boyfriend Machine Gun Kelly backstage at the Billboard Music Awards after very public X-rated display In a video of the pair later at the ceremony, Megan, 35, appears to mouth: 'What the f**k' while speaking to Kelly, 31, who can be seen standing alongside her. Megan Fox appears to swear and looks frosty with Machine Gun Kelly

Doja Cat wows in an edgy monochrome ensemble while the night's big winner The Weeknd puts on a suave display at Billboard Awards after-party The Say So hitmaker, 25, transformed from her red carpet ensemble into a chic black and white coord, while the Blinding Lights singer, 31, was suave in a suit Doja Cat wows at Billboard Awards after-party

Dixie D'Amelio and boyfriend Noah Beck look loved up as TikTok stars make their first red carpet appearance together at the Billboard Music Awards Dixie D'Amelio and her boyfriend Noah Beck made their first red carpet appearance together as a couple, since they began dating back in September 2020. Dixie D'Amelio and Noah Beck make their red carpet debut at the BBMAs

Doja Cat arrives at Billboard Music Awards after-party in voluminous silver ensemble with graphic jacket The rapper, 25, had performed the track Kiss Me More with Sza during the awards show in LA. Doja Cat arrives at Billboard Music Awards party in silver ensemble

Kathryn Hahn brings attitude in white corset with black mohair jacket and trousers at Billboard Music Awards The actress, 47, stunned on the red carpet in a stylish ensemble by Thom Browne. Kathryn Hahn pairs corset with trousers at Billboard Music Awards

The Weeknd rolls out a fleet of classic cars for his performance of Save Your Tears at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards The Weeknd was the big winner at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards, taking home 10 awards including Artist of the Year, but he also turned in one of the night's most memorable performances. The Weeknd rolls out a fleet of classic cars at the Billboard Awards

Chelsea Handler puts her figure on display in curve-hugging yellow dress as she brings the glamour to the 2021 Billboard Music Awards The television host, 46, looked incredible showcasing her figure in a skintight yellow number that hugged her incredible body. Chelsea Handler puts her figure on display in curve-hugging dress

'Someone will be fired': Twitter reacts as Billboard Music Awards plays track by Post Malone instead of DaBaby and Roddy Ricch during award for Top Rap Song The North Carolina native, 29, acknowledged the flub as he accepted the honors at the outdoor event held at the Microsoft Theater in Los Angeles, saying, 'It's me, It's me, I'll live with that.' Billboard Awards plays wrong track as DaBaby and Roddy Ricch win

Hold On, We're Going Home! Drake dedicates his Artist Of The Decade honor to sobbing son Adonis, three, at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards Drake brought his son Adonis, three, who he shares with Sophie Brussaux, to accept the Artist of the Decade award at the Billboard Music Awards on Sunday. Drake dedicates his Artist Of The Decade honor to son Adonis

Megan Fox nearly bares all in a strappy body, grabs boyfriend Machine Gun Kelly's CROTCH and licks his black tongue in wildly inappropriate PDA on Billboard Music Awards red carpet The Transformers actress, 35, and Bloody Valentine singer, 31, caused quite the stir as they groped each other and passionately made out right on the red carpet. Megan Fox and MGK push the limits of PDA at the Billboard Music Awards

American Idol alum Gabby Barrett wins three Billboard Music Awards including Top Country Female Artist The 21-year-old also took home the trophies for Top Collaboration and Top Song for her breakout single I Hope featuring Charlie Puth. American Idol alum Gabby Barrett wins three Billboard Music Awards

Pink, 41, and daughter Willow Sage, 9, steal the show by soaring above the stage during stunning aerial show, as they lead epic performances at 2021 Billboard Music Awards Before receiving the Icon Award at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards, the legendary Pink stole the show with an acrobatic performance of Cover Me In Sunshine alongside daughter Willow Sage. Pink steals the show with acrobatic version of Cover Me In Sunshine

'You took us to church, to the symphony, a candle light dinner and couples therapy!': Michelle Obama praises Alicia Keys' musical range in 2021 Billboard Music Awards intro The former First Lady remembered her first time listening to the artist as she introduced her for a special performance celebrating the 20th anniversary of her debut album, Songs In A Minor. Michelle Obama praises Alicia Keys' at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards

Gabrielle Union dazzles in figure-hugging low-cut Prada gown at Billboard Music Awards in LA The actress, 48, carried a pale pink Prada purse, sported pink polish on her toe nails and was made up with soft pink lip color. Gabrielle Union dazzles in Prada gown at Billboard Music Awards in LA

DJ Khaled joined by H.E.R. and Migos kick off the 2021 Billboard Music Awards by performing We're Going Crazy in front of HUNDREDS of fans The 2021 Billboard Music Awards kicked off with a fun-filled live performance by DJ Khaled, who was joined by H.E.R. and Migos to sing their hit We're Going Crazy. DJ Khaled joined by H.E.R. and Migos kick off the Billboard Awards

The Weeknd sweeps the board with TEN trophies at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards... after his mega-hit album was completely snubbed by the Grammys The Weeknd kicked off the 2021 Billboard Music Awards by winning Top Hot 100 Artist after previously being snubbed by the Grammy Awards. Nick Jonas hosted after injuring his ribs. 2021 Billboard Music Awards Winners!

H.E.R. puts on a fiery display in a red spangled jumpsuit as she arrives at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards... where she's nominated for Top R&B Song H.E.R., 23, heated up the 2021 Billboard Music Awards when she hit the red carpet in a sparkling jumpsuit decorated with spangles. She's competing in the Top R&B Song category. H.E.R. rocks a red spangled jumpsuit at 2021 Billboard Music Awards

Red (hot) carpet PDA! Nick Jonas and Priyanka Chopra can't keep their eyes off each other as they arrive at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards Nick Jonas and Priyanka Chopra hit the red carpet in style before fulfilling their hosting and presenting duties at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards. Nick Jonas and Priyanka Chopra hit the red carpet at Billboard Awards

Alicia Keys showcases taut abs in pink crop top and pants with enormous train at Billboard Music Awards Keys returned to the awards show to celebrate 20 years since the release of her debut album Songs in A Minor and she'll perform a medley of her hits during the telecast. Alicia Keys stands out in pink crop top and pants at Billboard Awards

Pink poses with her children Jameson and Willow before receiving Icon Award at the Billboard Music Awards The 41-year-old pop star will also perform an eight-minute set during Sunday night's NBC telecast Pink poses with children Jameson and Willow at Billboard Music Awards

The Jonas Brothers and Marshmello rehearse new music ahead of their Billboard Music Awards performance The Jonas Brothers and Marshmello rehearsed their track Leave Before You Love Me ahead of their 2021 Billboard Music Awards performance. The track is one Sophie Turner is 'f***ing obsessed' with The Jonas Brothers and Marshmello rehearse for Billboard Music Awards

Pink commands the stage and host Nick Jonas brushes up on his lines during rehearsals for Sunday's 2021 Billboard Music Awards One of music's biggest nights is taking place on Sunday, and these music superstars are leading the charge of those preparing for the blockbuster event. Pink and Nick Jonas lead rehearsals for 2021 Billboard Music Awards

Drake's mother Sandi Graham and son Adonis will both be in the audience when the rapper is named the Artist of the Decade at Billboard Music Awards The 34-year-old rapper is set to receive the Artist of the Decade award at the forthcoming ceremony, and TMZ reported that his parent and child would watch him accept the distinction. Drake's mother and son will attend the Billboard Music Awards

Pink will receive the ICON Award at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards: 'It's a true "pinch me" moment and I feel blessed' Pink will receive the ICON Award at the 2021 Billboard Awards, becoming the ninth artist in history to receive the honor. NBC and dick clark productions announced the news on Tuesday. Pink will receive the ICON Award at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards

Nick Jonas is set to host the 2021 Billboard Music Awards live from Los Angeles in May... as The Weeknd leads the nominations list Dick clark productions and NBC today announced on Friday that The Voice coach is set to host the 2021 Billboard Music Awards live from the Microsoft Theater in Los Angeles on May 23. Nick Jonas is set to host the 2021 Billboard Music Awards

Morgan Wallen not welcome at Billboard Awards ceremony 'in any capacity' after being caught using N-word on video, despite being nominated in five categories Morgan Wallen was caught using the N-word in a video posted by a neighbor, which resulted in numerous career consequences for the country music superstar. Morgan Wallen not welcome at Billboard Awards ceremony next month

The Weeknd leads the 2021 Billboard Music Awards with 16 nominations... following his shocking Grammy snub The Weeknd is the leading nominee at the 2021 Billboard Music Awards with more than 16 nods for his latest album After Hours, which was snubbed by the Grammys. The Weeknd leads the 2021 Billboard Music Awards with 16 nominations

2021 Billboard Music Awards will air Sunday, May 23 on NBC... seven months after the 2020 awards NBC has announced the date for their 2021 Billboard Music Awards, happening just seven months after the delayed 2020 Billboard Music Awards took place. 2021 Billboard Music Awards will air Sunday, May 23 on NBC

Chrissy Teigen pens a heartbreaking essay about losing son Jack at five months pregnant: 'I cried a little at first, then went into full blown convulsions' 'I had no idea when I would be ready to write this. Part of me thought it would be early on, when I was still really feeling the pain of what happened,' began the cover girl as she detailed her loss. Chrissy Teigen pens a heartbreaking essay about losing son Jack

Addison Rae opens up about her BIG mistake presenting at the 2020 Billboard Music Awards Just under two weeks after a rather big blunder at the 2020 Billboard Music Awards, Addison Rae is explaining herself. Addison Rae opens up about her BIG mistake at the Billboard Awards

Doja Cat teases a glimpse of her toned torso in a racy black bra and cut-out silk kimono as she turns 25 in style at PrettyLittleThing birthday party The Say So hitmaker looked incredible for the lavish bash as she teased a glimpse of her toned torso in a racy black bra. Doja Cat turns 25 in style at PrettyLittleThing birthday party

John Legend dotes on daughter Luna, four, on Sunday outing in exclusive Bel-Air following wife Chrissy Teigen's pregnancy loss He and wife Chrissy Teigen have very publicly shared the heartbreaking loss of their son Jack. John Legend dotes on daughter Luna, four, on Sunday outing in Bel-Air

Kanye West celebrates his Billboard Awards success after scooping four gongs... amid claims he was 'reported to police for breaking quarantine rules in London' The rapper, 43, took to Instagram to 'thank God, fans and all of my Christians,' for his success after the awards on Wednesday, with gongs including Top Gospel Artist and Top Gospel Album. Kanye West celebrates his Billboard Awards success

Chrissy Teigen heads to the shops with husband John Legend in LA... after breaking her silence to reveal she's 'quiet but okay' following baby loss Chrissy Teigen and John Legend surfaced from self-isolation in Los Angeles this Friday to run an errand or two. The 41-year-old singer and the 34-year-old model kept their masks on. Chrissy Teigen and John Legend emerge from lockdown to shop in LA
